You are about to find feminized indica and sativa seeds, feminized single strains... The best feminized seeds for sale are here, let's discover them.

Feminized seeds, why buy them?

Feminized seeds have a crucial advantage: they have a lot of cannabinoids, but this is not the only advantage of these genetics.

- It increases the chances of developing cannabis plants with more power and aroma. These are key factors to produce the best effects during its use...

- You don't have to worry about separating males and females, so you are on the safe side with total comfort. In other words, there is no danger of fertilization. In addition, in Delicious Seeds we select them in a particularly careful way so that you do not get any surprise.

- Maximum variety. If you take a look at our feminized cannabis seeds, you will realize that you have many more alternatives compared to the regular ones.

Feminized strains are also usually photoperiodic, so they depend on the amount of hours of light or darkness they receive to germinate (more or less time).

If your space is nature, and you are looking for outdoor feminized marijuana seeds, these plants usually bloom at the end of summer, when the days are getting shorter. Indoors, these plants remain in a vegetative state until the grower reduces the hours of light to induce flowering.

Fem seeds, choose yours

At Delicious Seeds you can buy the fem seed that best suits your needs. We have developed a large number of strains which cover all possible features, allowing you to try gradually an infinite number of options.

You will become an expert of feminized cannabis seeds. In addition, new strains are continuously emerging, so buying them in this way brings you especially close to end up trying the female variety that suits your tastes.

Female weed seeds, what should you consider?

Female weed seeds are easier to grow compared to other types. Even so, it is important to take into account a series of specific cares such as the ones detailed below:
If you are thinking about outdoor cannabis seeds, before doing so, it is necessary to take into account the climatic conditions, as well as the season of the year.

Female plants need a certain amount of light to flower properly. Therefore, we recommend planting these strains in spring and harvesting them in autumn, especially to ensure that they are not exposed to frost.

Indoors, we can control the hours of light and darkness that feminized marijuana seeds receive more easily. This is usually done when the plants have reached a suitable height (about half of the desired final height).

The right humidity level for these plants depends on the stage of growth they are in.

In their vegetative stage, the plants need a more humid environment, while in the flowering stage we recommend reducing the humidity to 50%. Remember not to exceed the humidity if you want to avoid mildew.

Temperature? No particularities here. We continue with a temperate around 21 degrees.

Now you have everything you need to buy feminized marijuana seeds at Delicious Seeds. You are just one click away from enjoying a quality harvest.
